    Class Description
    About
    This class is for the about dialog.
    Element
    This class is a template for an Element object.
    ElementList
    This class sets up the arraylist for all compounds and elements, which are read in from a text file.
    GameBoard
    This class is the main game panel and in-game actions are processed here.
    HighScore
    This manages and manipulates the highscore of the game.
    Instructions
    This method is the Instructions.
    LevelSelection
    Creates the level selection screen where the user will have a choice to choose their difficulty or return to the main menu.
    Menu
    Creates the main menu panel which consists of the game name and button options that the player can access.
    PlayerName
    Creates a dialog to ask the player for their name and stores their name.
    Print
    Used to create methods that will print text for the highscore menu.
    SplashScreen
    Creates a panel that is used for the splash screen of the program.
    TetristryApp
    This is the driver class for Tetristry.
    Time
    This class is used as the timer for the game.
    Tutorial
    Creates a panel that is used as the tutorial to teach the player the basics of chemistry nomenclature.
